<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer7661346729193145168">Sandie Jones has worked as a freelance journalist for over twenty years, and has written for publications including the Sunday Times, Woman’s Weekly and the Daily Mail. She lives in London with her husband and three children. <i>The Other Woman</i> is her debut novel.</span>

</div>
